## Supabase Edge Functions Secrets (Configure in Supabase Dashboard)

These are already configured in your Supabase project:
- `LYGOS_API_KEY` - Lygos payment gateway API key
- `RESEND_API_KEY` - Resend email service API key
- `MISTRAL_API_KEY` - Mistral AI API key for product descriptions and chat assistant
- `SUPABASE_URL` - Auto-configured
- `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` - Auto-configured
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` - Auto-configured

